data.description: This immaculately maintained 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom, 3 car garage ranch home is located in the popular Tregaron neighborhood! Beautiful hardwood floors in the entry and kitchen are coupled with newer main level carpeting and well-cared for wood cabinetry and trim throughout. Most all main level windows have been replaced, as well as the a/c unit, microwave, and oven. The primary suite has a tray ceiling in the bedroom, a skylight in the bathroom, double sink vanity, and private toilet room, as well as a spacious walk-in closet! With five bedrooms, a bonus flex room, and 12 foot ceilings in the oversized living room, this home has all the space you need--and more! This beautiful, one-owner home is highlighted by a newly stained covered deck, overlooking a fully fenced backyard on an ideal corner lot. Schedule your private tour today!
